News Corp names pres / COO , management office . News Corp said on Tuesday that Peter Chernin has been appointed president and chief operating officer , and Chase Carey has been named co - chief operating officer . The company said North American operations of News Corp will be consolidated under its Fox Group , of which Chernin will be chairman and chief executive . Carey will continue as chairman and chief executive of Fox Television Group , which falls under the Fox Group . News Corp said it also has established an Office of the Chairman , which will have management responsibility for its worldwide operations . 
